---
/*
  Clove hitch illustration for the Principles section.
  SVG asset lives at public/images/clove-hitch.svg — referenced from the
  site root via /images/... (public/ is Astro's static root).
*/
---

<figure class="clove-hitch">
  <span class="clove-hitch-label">Jeremy&rsquo;s Principles of Design</span>
  <img
    class="clove-hitch-svg"
    src="/images/clove-hitch.svg"
    alt="A line drawing of a clove hitch tied around a vertical post."
    width="260"
    height="260"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <figcaption class="clove-hitch-caption">
    <p>&ldquo;The clove hitch is an incredibly simple knot. Once under tension, it holds until the rope breaks.&rdquo;</p>
  </figcaption>
</figure>
